"content": "<h2>Marriage to cousins</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num36:11\">NUM 36:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr23:22\">1CH 23:22</a></p>\n<h2>Family responsibilities undertaken by cousins where there were no closer relatives</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:7\">EST 2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:47-Lev25:49\">LEV 25:47–25:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:6-Jer32:12\">JER 32:6–32:12</a></p>\n<h2>Cousins mentioned in Scripture</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:10\">COL 4:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:4\">LEV 10:4</a></p>",
